{"tid":576498,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有時候覺得好多陰謀論都係真","createTime":"2018-03-01T02:56:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T05:55:09.000Z","uid":36097,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8770c5f3f711ffb7e702fcc0e23664a99a0e095d","tid":576498,"uid":36097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T02:56:32.000Z","msg":"其實唔止係依家，好多時睇完documentary或者美劇，都會覺得呢個世界其實係充滿好多陰謀、勾結。不過過一排又會唔記得哂，因為自己根本冇野做到，或者說服自己諗多左。<br />\n<br />\n例如，啱啱無聊睇左套叫What the health ，講好多好多疾病預防協會、「非牟利組織」都有隱瞞某D食物會致病，甚至係網站推廣個D食物。當主持人問返佢地，D負責人一係拒絕訪問，一係發老脾。原來D疾病預防協會係由D肉商、加工食品商、KFC贊助。好似south park D 劇情咁，真係好黑暗。<br />\n<br />\n咁我又諗，究竟呢個世界係咁黑暗，定係我諗多左 + documentary一定有立場嫁啦，因為D食品商有錢，所以想盡下「社會責任」？<br />\n<br />\n有冇人有睇下 documentary，講下呢個世界仲有咩陰謀、勾結？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/030643_1eb5d3067f8b25c9f26a6ae1a8aef003.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F030643_1eb5d3067f8b25c9f26a6ae1a8aef003.png&h=8544e43b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/030648_bb58f3ce25eb57125fcc87af3a21a817.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F030648_bb58f3ce25eb57125fcc87af3a21a817.png&h=20c81975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/030305_4bee15e26543ac77522c4abdcf971df1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F030305_4bee15e26543ac77522c4abdcf971df1.png&h=ec582c29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"706ff8867053a8abe443c464c0e40c233e143143","tid":576498,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T03:01:24.000Z","msg":"近排睇左套叫「Fed Up」，講食物中的糖、肥胖、與食品公司如何誤導人類"},{"pid":"4bfcc2b9108566fe5661bd192ac2b4a6e92d795f","tid":576498,"uid":104171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":